title: BRIEF-Sartorius Stedim Biotech And Penn State University Entered Into Collaborative Partnership

text:
April 16, 2018 / 12:46 PM / Updated 22 minutes ago BRIEF-Sartorius Stedim Biotech And Penn State University Entered Into Collaborative Partnership Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 16 (Reuters) - SARTORIUS STEDIM BIOTECH SA: 
* SARTORIUS STEDIM BIOTECH AND PENN STATE UNIVERSITY ENTERED INTO COLLABORATIVE PARTNERSHIP TO ADVANCE MULTIDISCIPLINARY TEACHING AND RESEARCH IN BIOTECHNOLOGY Source text : bit.ly/2qygOm0 Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
